title: Spence vs Crawford HIGHLIGHTS: JULY 29, 2023 | PBC on Showtime PPV
tags: Boxing|PBC|premier boxing champions|ko|tko|knockouts|fighter|boxer|mayweather|al haymon|showtime boxing|wilder|thurman|spence|porter|broner|fighting|best of|highlights|wbo|wba|wbc|ibo|ibf|boxing highlights|errol spence hr|terence crawford|spence vs crawford|crawford spence|terence bud crawford|spence crawford|premier boxing|pbc|fight highlights|undisputed|ppv highlights|terence|terence crawford highlights|terence crawford vs errol spence jr
description: Undefeated three-division champion Terence ‚ÄúBud‚Äù Crawford emphatically stamped his place in the history books with a ninth-round TKO over the previously unbeaten Errol ‚ÄúThe Truth‚Äù Spence Jr. to become the first undisputed welterweight champion of the four-belt era in the SHOWTIME PPV main event Saturday night from T-Mobile Arena in Las Vegas in an event presented by Premier Boxing Champions. ‚ÄúIt means everything because of who I took the belts from,‚Äù said Crawford. ‚ÄúThey talked bad about me. They said I wasn‚Äôt good enough and I couldn‚Äôt beat these welterweights. I just kept my head to the sky and kept praying to God that I would get the opportunity to show the world how great Terence Crawford is. Tonight, I believe I showed how great I am.‚Äù ‚ÄúHe was just better tonight,‚Äù said Spence. ‚ÄúHe was using the jab. My timing was a little bit off. He was just the better man tonight.‚Äù In addition to adding the WBC, WBA and IBF titles to his WBO belt, Crawford became the first male fighter to become an undisputed champion in two weight classes, having previously won all four belts at 140-pounds. In a fight where Spence had already been down three times, Crawford‚Äôs ninth round onslaught of hooks forced referee Harvey Dock to wave off the action 2:32 in the frame. After years of build-up, Spence came out aggressively in the opening round, jabbing and attacking Crawford‚Äôs body. Crawford, who is known for fighting from both the southpaw and orthodox stances, fought primarily as a southpaw and scored his first knockdown in round two with a powerful right cross that caught Spence off balance and sent him down for the first time in his career. ‚ÄúWe practice that,‚Äù said Crawford. ‚ÄúNormally in camp we do a flick and jab. But we knew that wasn‚Äôt going to work with Errol Spence because he‚Äôs durable, he‚Äôs strong. So we had to practice a strong firm jab. The jab hit him and stopped him in his tracks.‚Äù ‚ÄúHe was just throwing the hard jab,‚Äù said Spence. ‚ÄúHe was timing with his jab. His timing was just on point. I wasn‚Äôt surprised by his speed or his accuracy. It was everything I thought.‚Äù Spence came out in round three determined to turn the tide after the knockdown, throwing big shots, including a left hook that landed cleanly early. However, Crawford was able to withstand the attack and showed his precision by landing a clean counter right that again staggered Spence. ‚ÄúErrol Spence is a tremendous talent and he‚Äôs got a great jab,‚Äù said Crawford. ‚ÄúWe were worried about the jab coming in because that‚Äôs how he sets up all of his shots.  Our main focus was the jab. You take away his best attribute. The rest is history.‚Äù In round seven, Crawford dropped Spence twice, once with a clean right uppercut early on and again late in the round with a right hook. Crawford led 79-70 on all three cards at the time of the stoppage and dominated the CompuBox stats with an 185 to 96 advantage in punches landed and an astounding 50% connect rate. Post-fight, Crawford showed his respect for Spence stepping up to the plate and making the super fight happen and spoke to the historic nature of the matchup, while Spence expressed his interest in a rematch later this year. ‚ÄúWe gotta do it again,‚Äù said Spence. ‚ÄúI‚Äôm going to be a lot better. It‚Äôll be a lot closer. It‚Äôll probably be in December and the end of the year. I say we gotta do it again.‚Äù ‚ÄúLike I said before, I only dreamed of being a world champion,‚Äù said Crawford. ‚ÄúI‚Äôm an overachiever. Nobody believed in me when I was coming up, but I made everybody a believer. I want to thank Spence and his team because without him none of this would have been possible.‚Äù#TerenceCrawford #ErrolSpenceJr #SpenceCrawfordVisit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: https://pbcham.ps/FightAlertsFOLLOW US:https://twitter.com/premierboxinghttps://instagram.com/premierboxinghttps://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

title: r/place 2023 full timelapse (4k, lossless quality)
tags: [none]
description: LOSSLESS DOWNLOAD (6GB): https://hobune.stream/f/place-2023-lossless.movThis upload is not an endorsement of Reddit as a platform, I made it because all of the other uploads are low-quality and none offer a lossless pixel-perfect download for content creators and others to use and zoom into.This video was made by gathering the full r/place canvas PNGs directly from Reddit's servers for every 30 seconds ending up with a total of 15323 frames, which when ran at 60fps results in a 1800x speed for the timelapse. The download is a 3000x2000 video encoded from the individual PNGs into the QTRLE codec, which preserves RGB video losslessly and is supported by most modern video editors.The YouTube upload's resolution was extended to 3240x2160 to make sure lower resultions re-encoded by YouTube look acceptable. The pixels are still 1:1 mapped with padding around them as opposed to scaled up to fullscreen like the official Reddit videos did (very ugly for pixel stuff!). The YouTube re-encode was uploaded as QTRLE, although what you see will probably be encoded into something like vp9 or av1 by YouTube themselves and there is nothing I can do about that, but it should still look quite decent.You DO NOT need to credit me if you use this, but I beg you to use nearest neighbor scaling when zooming into the footage because ugly bilinearly scaled pixel art is very ugly.Chapters0:00 - Beginning0:54 - 1st expansion1:03 - New colors added1:26 - 2nd expansion1:56 - 3rd expansion2:34 - 4th expansion + more colors2:49 - 5th expansion3:20 - 6th expansion4:13 - Only grayscale pixels4:15 - Only white pixelsMusic: C418 - Concerete Halls (please buy at https://c418.bandcamp.com/album/minecraft-volume-beta)
